Aaron Ramsey's goal: BBC Radio 5 live commentary
Listen to BBC Radio 5 live commentary of Aaron Ramsey's stunning long-range strike inArsenal's 4-1 Champions League win over Galatasaray.Commentator Conor McNamara describes the strike as "one of the goals of the season" while Arsenal bossArsene Wenger says he thought Ramsey was overly optimistic when half-volleying, but the Frenchman was proved "wrong".The Gunners were dominant in Istanbul but the emphatic scoreline was not enough to claim top spot in Group D as Borussia Dortmund avoided defeat against Anderlecht in their final group game.Available to UK users only.